Kenosha County Circuit Court Judge Bruce Schroeder was speaking about the court's plans for lunch when he made a joke about the supply chain issues at Long Beach Harbor in California.

"I hope the Asian food isn't coming ... isn't on one of those boats from Long Beach Harbor," he said.

Video of the innocuous joke was posted to Twitter by CNN reporter Kyung Lah. Julia Vargas Jones, a field producer for CNN, replied that "the media room let out a collective gasp."
